reviewText: great Gus and Felcity episodes, also liked how felicity figured out what is most important

This includes 2 episodes, the first,"A Dark and Stormy Night", is a crazy adventure in which Sara, Felicity, Felix and Gus get mixed up with some jewel theives. Christopher Reeves plays a good bad guy and the lady who is his partner is good too. The storyline is a bit confusing but it is entertaining and mysterious!
